Context engineering:
	- Maintain a knowledge graph of projects and research
	- smart 'read' tool: read, but with an optional natural language 'scope' parameter
	for reducing noise. should the user want to read auth.ts for a specific provider example,
	simply provide 'auth provider <provider> implementation' as the scope. the tool will return
	the relevant portions. if not included, will default to the entire file. also has line-by-line
	and regular grep-like features
	- index files and perform some preliminary retrieval step for some actions. depending on the complexity,
	this can include a lot of information. otherwise, works as 'just-in-time' context.
	- probably add a reranker as well

